SQL_STMT_U.val: select count(*) from :1/BPIV where BPIV_BTCH_ID = :2 and BPIV_INVO_NO = 0 for fetch only
select count(*) from :1/SCHI where SCHI_SCHT_NO = :2 for fetch only
select count(*) from :1/SCHI where SCHI_SCHT_NO = :2 for fetch only

select count(*) from (select BTPC_DEBC_NO from :1/BTPC where BTPC_BTCH_ID = :2 and BTPC_DEBC_NO > 0 and not(exists(select * from :1/SILO where SILO_DEBC_NO = BTPC_DEBC_NO)) group by BTPC_DEBC_NO) as T for fetch only
select distinct BTPC_DEBC_NO from :1/BTPC where BTPC_DEBC_NO > 0 and not (exists(select * from :1/SILO where SILO_DEBC_NO = BTPC_DEBC_NO)) and BTPC_BTCH_ID = :2 order by BTPC_DEBC_NO

select count(*) from (select SCHI_DEBC_NO from :1/SCHI where SCHI_SCHT_NO in (:2, :3) and SCHI_DEBC_NO > 0 and SCHI_INVDELETED = 'N' and SCHI_INVAMOUNTI <0 and not(exists(select * from :1/SILO where SILO_DEBC_NO = SCHI_DEBC_NO)) group by SCHI_DEBC_NO) as T for fetch only

select distinct SCHI_DEBC_NO from :1/SCHI where SCHI_DEBC_NO > 0 and SCHI_INVDELETED = 'N' and SCHI_INVAMOUNTI < 0 and not (exists(select * from :1/SILO where SILO_DEBC_NO = SCHI_DEBC_NO)) and SCHI_SCHT_NO = :2 order by SCHI_DEBC_NO

Text.val: -- Calculate and book the max stockfinance
... determine time difference if dates different
... determine total seconds (current row)
... determine total seconds (next row)
... calculate time difference from date/time started of next row - date/time started of current row
... convert time difference in seconds to time picture
... Set time to 99 hours , to avoid an overflow, in case time difference >= 100 hours
... store time difference to database (to alpha field, time fields in DB do not support times > 24:00:00)
